synergyviewcommons.collections

Interface CollectionChangeListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnnotationPropertyViewPart, AttributeNode, CodingRoot, ProjectAttributeRootNode, SubjectRowModel

    public interface CollectionChangeListener
    The listener interface for receiving collectionChange events. The class that is interested in processing a collectionChange event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addCollectionChangeListener method. When the collectionChange event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.
    See Also:
    CollectionChangeEvent
